sentences: Lynch and Harding released a seven inch split together on Joyful Noise Recordings in 2015.
‚ÄùThe self-titled Debut was released on Joyful Noise Recordings in August 2013, with the single ("Redrum") premiering in the AV Club and in InSound's weekly mixtape.
The video for "Redrum", directed by David Yow, premiered in Rolling Stone, and Spin the following month.
Dumb Numbers toured with the Lemonheads, My Bloody Valentine, and Sebadoh during the latter half of 2013.
